(VisionEduHub - Architecture and Deployment Brief) Tj
T*
(Generated: 2026-03-01 20:47 UTC) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1\) Product Intent) Tj
T*
(- Arabic-first Smart Teacher's Assistant for classroom writing quality.) Tj
T*
(- Detect grammar/spelling issues and rhetoric weaknesses.) Tj
T*
(- Return improved draft plus creative alternatives.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2\) Recommended MVP Stack) Tj
T*
(- Frontend: RTL dashboard \(Liquid Glass and Spatial UI direction\).) Tj
T*
(- Backend: Node.js API with isolated analyzer module.) Tj
T*
(- Data: PostgreSQL schema with typed enums and indexed analytics.) Tj
T*
(- AI: Optional OpenAI augmentation; rule-based fallback is always available.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3\) Layered Architecture) Tj
T*
(- Presentation Layer: src/client/*) Tj
T*
(- Application Layer: src/server/index.js) Tj
T*
(- NLP and AI Layer: src/server/analyzer.js) Tj
T*
(- Data Layer: database/schema.sql) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4\) Database Highlights) Tj
T*
(- Core tables: users, lessons, analytics.) Tj
T*
(- Extended MVP tables: lesson_enrollments, student_submissions.) Tj
T*
(- Governance: constraints, timestamps, indexes, RLS enabled.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5\) Security Controls) Tj
T*
(- Role segmentation \(admin, teacher, student\).) Tj
T*
(- Input length limits and strict JSON parsing.) Tj
T*
(- Minimal PII in analytics payloads.) Tj
T*
(- Ready for JWT auth and tenant-scoped RLS policies.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6\) Scalability Plan) Tj
T*
(- Add async workers for heavy analysis workloads.) Tj
T*
(- Partition analytics by time windows.) Tj
T*
(- Add Redis counters and read replicas for dashboards.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7\) Deployment Steps) Tj
T*
(1. Install runtime dependencies and start API service.) Tj
T*
(2. Provision PostgreSQL and apply database/schema.sql.) Tj
T*
(3. Set env vars: PORT, OPENAI_API_KEY \(optional\).) Tj
T*
(4. Configure reverse proxy, TLS, and observability.) Tj
T*
(5. Run smoke checks for /api/health and /api/analyze-text.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Output artifact:) Tj
